item.dc:creator: @primadude Primadude
item.description:
@primadude wrote:

Under ‘case 132:’ in your client.java, add:

if (objectID == ####) { addItem(####, 1); }

Replace the two '####'s with the IDs of the tree objects and the IDs of the fruit items.
